thread.title: Tammy G.
thread.title_full: Master Supplements, Inc. reviewed by Tammy G.

author: Tammy G.
title: Tammy G.
text: Not only am I impressed with the quality of the products but I am even more impressed with the quality of service! I have been using Master Supplements probiotics and digestive enzymes for one year and from day one, Sophie has been educating me on the products to find the exact fit for me and my family. I have referred numerous people to this company and they are all completely satisfied with not only the quality of the product but the quality of the people who stand behind it.
